## Verification Session: 2026-03-24 (Phase 4 Slice 4.3 - Minimal Read-Model Projector)

### Scope
- Replace the reporting projector placeholder with a minimal non-authoritative read model
- Add replay/rebuild proof from persisted `outbox_events`
- Close the loan-topic routing gap so lending events are not silently published to the ledger fallback topic

### Changes Applied
- `V17__read_model_event_feed.sql`:
  - added `read_model_event_feed` for replayable, non-authoritative event history
  - indexed by aggregate and occurrence time for dashboard/history use
- `KafkaConfig`:
  - added `loan-events` topic definition
- `OutboxEventPublisher`:
  - routes `LOAN_*` events to `loan-events`
- `ReadModelProjector`:
  - replaced placeholder with envelope-aware projection logic
  - subscribes to `account/transfer/payment/deposit/loan/ledger` topics
  - skips legacy/non-envelope payloads safely
